reviewText: I have been waiting quite a while for this to come out and even though my time playing is not much i am already pleased that i bought this game. Once i complete this entirely ill most likely buy Dungeoning. This is a really great game. Thanks Nick and Tony!

reviewText: Fantastic game, it's been a while since I had so much fun with a platformer.\nThe game is a no-nonsense platformer, simple and to the point graphics and physics. The game concentrates on the core: The level design and elements are brilliant. The sountrack is C64 sid style genius. High replay value as levels can be played for speedrun times or for exploration to find all secret areas.
